'''Chelsea''' is one of the cheerleaders who came to the ER after falling during a routine.

==History==
Chelsea came into the ER after a fall during a cheerleading routine. She had broken her arm, so it was braced and bandaged from her wrist to her elbow.

When a teammate, [[Maxine Hewitt|Maxine]], needed surgery for a heart condition, [[Lisa Wilcox|Lisa]], [[Danielle (All Eyez on Me)|Danielle]], and Chelsea argued about the situation. Stephanie then rallied the whole team to become a team and be supportive for Maxine. They then went to visit her in her hospital room.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
She is friends with her fellow cheerleaders. She supported Lisa's decision to remove Danielle and Maxine from the team.
